pro_course_detail.description:
General Course of Business Russian for students with level starting from A2. Includes such topics as:
- State organization and economics in Russia;
- Business Ethics;
- Writing a business letter;
- Preparing for business calls and business negotiations;
- Advertising in Russia;
- Business documents;

All training materials are provided.

1) Чтение произведения (Lectura de la obra);
2) Лексико-грамматический анализ текста (Análisis gramatical y análisis léxico);
3) Анализ содержания (Análisis del contenido)
